{"tid":585791,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人放假會去做兼職？","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T10:38:09.000Z","uid":20241,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5c5429b0c630d5e900aa81dc5de213dbdc0e80","tid":585791,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"星期六日想搵多些少錢<br />\n咁平時做文職 主要都係睇住啲contractor 安排人做野為主<br />\n但去到做炒散 做樓面 俾啲讀唔成書既廢中點我做野 有時又要你做on9野 又要守埋曬啲弱智規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要個班全職做呢啲低賤工既垃圾見有pt就推埋自己個份俾你叫你做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環境又惡劣屌你老尾休息室竟然係廁所隔離間雜物房又唔通風又有朕味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要想問咩兼職係比較輕鬆又唔駛俾班無學歷既廢柴點黎點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208fe34980045be2218847d9c24d2d1aa50c373d","tid":585791,"uid":162357,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"放工/放假去做freelance 體適能教練，一對一/group class教下人做gym減下肥<br />\n都做左2年幾，習慣哂早出晚歸，營營役役既生活"},{"pid":"bcecd82f0a45d02a65122ed572cab176671b8686","tid":585791,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"Party room 不過你應該會嫌人工低 通常得四五十一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703b94329730452c8f93e4287b5905556877fe58","tid":585791,"uid":12466,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"有份Sale性質工招聘人手中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPart Time(Sat&amp;Sun) <br />\n時薪$60up<br />\nFull Time都請緊<br />\n底薪一萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想了解詳情嘅巴打絲打不妨telegram我<br />\n@LiHKG_AgentD"},{"pid":"cee075f55bf91b410c4242a6216de6cc273ee4ca","tid":585791,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"展覽會helper 囉 <br />\n行行企企舉牌 室內又有冷氣 有break $5-60"},{"pid":"446e159dce2879d1a82d2d2082ba85875f0154e